title: kungen12321
author: kungen12321
content: Hi guys!I updated the firmware to the newest one. After that it didn`t start to hash anymore. I flashed it back to the older firmware but no success.What can be wrong?Thanks in adavnce!

comments.author: kungen12321
comments.body: I have downgraded and now Contacted them. They said it was a problem with my PSU. I bought a new one, but still the same problem, the miner doesn`t start hash.

comments.author: EastCoastASICRepair
comments.body: If all boards fail to init on the miner dashboard then they will need to be powered on a test fixture to determine the issue, whether it is temp sensor/other ICs failure or a bad chip.
